tes/2/2025/02/avowed-practical-pockets-treasure-map-solution-reward-4.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=828 828w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-practical-pockets-treasure-map-solution-reward-4.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1080 1080w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-practical-pockets-treasure-map-solution-reward-4.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1200 1200w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-practical-pockets-treasure-map-solution-reward-4.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1440 1440w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-practical-pockets-treasure-map-solution-reward-4.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1920 1920w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-practical-pockets-treasure-map-solution-reward-4.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2048 2048w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-practical-pockets-treasure-map-solution-reward-4.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2400 2400w\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-practical-pockets-treasure-map-solution-reward-4.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2400\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ccite\u003eImage: Obsidian Entertainment/Xbox Game Studios via Polygon\u003c/cite\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eInstead of approaching the rangers’ tower, take a path around the hill and to the northeast. You’re looking for a small alcove in the cliff under some lichen and giant blue mushrooms. Open the chest inside to find \u003cstrong\u003eHjilde’s Handy Hide\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp id=\"practical-pockets-reward\"\u003e\u003ch2\u003ePractical Pockets reward\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-practical-pockets-treasure-map-solution-reward-5.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0,0,100,100\" data-pswp-height=\"1440\" data-pswp-width=\"2560\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"A menu shows the reward for the Practical Pockets treasure map in Avowed\" data-chromatic=\"ignore\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"(max-width: 639px) 100vw, (max-width: 1023px) 50vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-practical-pockets-treasure-map-solution-reward-5.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=256 256w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-practical-pockets-treasure-map-solution-reward-5.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=376 376w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-practical-pockets-treasure-map-solution-reward-5.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=384 384w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-practical-pockets-treasure-map-solution-reward-5.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=415 415w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-practical-pockets-treasure-map-solution-reward-5.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=480 480w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-practical-pockets-treasure-map-solution-reward-5.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=540 540w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-practical-pockets-treasure-map-solution-reward-5.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=640 640w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-practical-pockets-treasure-map-solution-reward-5.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=750 750w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-practical-pockets-treasure-map-solution-reward-5.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=828 828w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-practical-pockets-treasure-map-solution-reward-5.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1080 1080w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-practical-pockets-treasure-map-solution-reward-5.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1200 1200w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-practical-pockets-treasure-map-solution-reward-5.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1440 1440w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-practical-pockets-treasure-map-solution-reward-5.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1920 1920w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-practical-pockets-treasure-map-solution-reward-5.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2048 2048w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-practical-pockets-treasure-map-solution-reward-5.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2400 2400w\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/02/avowed-practical-pockets-treasure-map-solution-reward-5.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2400\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ccite\u003eImage: Obsidian Entertainment/Xbox Game Studios via Polygon\u003c/cite\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eHjilde’s Handy Hide is, like the Stelgaer’s Price reward you get from the \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/avowed-guides/524369/intimidating-feline-codpiece-treasure-map-location-solution-reward\"\u003eIntimidating Feline Codpiece\u003c/a\u003e treasure map in \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/avowed-guides/521999/dawnshore-fast-travel-locations-camps-waypoints-beacons-all\"\u003eDawnshore\u003c/a\u003e, a full armor set. This one comes with some very useful bonuses. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHjilde’s Handy Hide stats\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e10% damage reduction\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e22 additional damage reduction\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e-20 maximum stamina\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e-20 maximum essence\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHjilde’s Handy Hide enchantment\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAll Seasons: -10% damage from fire, frost, and shock\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSurvivor: +40 maximum health\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003ePoison might be the most popular element in Emerald Stair, but you’ll start start facing enemies who deal fire, frost, or shock damage as well. Considering Hjilde’s Handy Hide starts as a second-level Fine quality item, it’s worth keeping this armor on hand, tempting though it may be to sell it.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003eFor more treasure maps in the \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/avowed-guides/522025/emerald-stair-fast-travel-locations-camps-beacons-all\"\u003eEmerald Stair\u003c/a\u003e region, see our solutions to the \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/e/524484\"\u003ePainter’s Regret\u003c/a\u003e and \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/e/524507\"\u003eEarthly Aegis\u003c/a\u003e treasure maps. Or see our list of all \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/avowed-guides/526878/treasure-maps-all-rewards-list\"\u003etreasure maps\u003c/a\u003e in \u003cem\u003eAvowed\u003c/em\u003e and our full \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/avowed-guides/522871/walkthrough-main-story-all-missions-list\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eAvowed\u003c/em\u003e walkthrough\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
